= TMuse reloaded = 

HOW TO :

* Get resources

  Graphs dicosyn & jdm  
  ! sync hubic for latest graphs
  
  Glaff 1.2.1
  
  $ make get_glaff
  

* install virtualenv and requirements

  $ virtualenv --system-site-packages venv
  $ source venv/bin/activate
  $ pip install -r requirements.txt

  $ make link_libjs

* create index ~5 minutes on my laptop
 
  loads jdm & dicosyn graphs, computes proxemies and stores in elasticsearch

  $ python index.py -i tmuse


* run app

  Edit index name in tmuse_es_app.py if you changed the index name default is 'tmuse'
  $ python app/tmuse_es_app.py


* browse app 

   only french verbs supported 'causer'
   $ firefox http://localhost:5000/causer
   



